defence
Via completing and defending the PhD thesis the student:
- is familiar with new research directions in his/her field of study;
- is capable of raising and formulating essential research problem in his/her field of study and providing original and argumentative solution for that problem;
- is capable of designing and conducting the research;
- is well informed about the process of publishing scientific articles in international pre-reviewed journals in his/her field of study;
- is capable of formulating results of his/her research into the form of internationally accepted publication;
- is able to argue and attend in discussions about his/her field of study both in speech and writing.Objectives/eesmärkid:  PhD students research aims at acquiring the skills and technical competence necessary for conducting research. Research must lead to completion of independent study project proposing a reasoned original solution to a substantial problem in a particular research field, which presupposes the publication of at least three research papers in leading international journals of the specialityLearning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon completing the reaserch within curricula Ph.D student has deep and wide undrestanding and knowledge in rresearch methodology in selected field of research. Ph.D student is able independently rise reaserch problems and offer solutions as through individual work as well through supervising. Ph. D student is able to present in written and in oral form his/her specific research as well actual reaserch problems related to specific field of study.
